rendering module features
 load textures
 create scene
  allocate memory for scene description
 move camera
  2D co-ordinates to center screen viewport on

rendering scene description
 background map
  tile size
  2D grid of tile texture IDs
 entities
  linked list AND hash table
   hashtable mapping entity ID to entity
   linked list of all entities
   hashtable mapping entity classes to linked lists of entities
  entity ID - used to reference entity from physics etc
  entity coordinates
  entity size
  entity texture
